title: Bloody Fetus Collection
description:
Here you have it. This is a collection of almost everything that singer/rapper Bloody Fetus has ever done. From his original stuff, to his parodies, to his cover tunes. This shit is nothing short of ate up. Quite possibly some of the funniest, sickest, and most demented stuff you&#039;ll ever hear. With songs like "She&#039;s My Retard Bitch", "Your Daughter Died a Virgin", "Give It To Me Granny", or "Abort That Baby", you really can&#039;t go wrong, unless you&#039;re a pussy.

A lot of people don&#039;t know it but Bloody Fetus is the original writer for the internet hit song "I&#039;m a Wigga", which is commonly mistaken to be by Weird Al for some odd reason. Don&#039;t believe it? Well, download this and hear it for yourself, he has a good number of songs that he sings using the same dorky voice he used for "I&#039;m a Wigga."

This file contains:

23 originals (but only the lyrics, maybe two or three original tracks)
23 cover songs (Some Good, some bad, some annoying, all butchered)
Bios of some of the various characters and voices
17 Pictures
2 Videos
